snippet.title: Kirby Street - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Kirby Street is finally available for download. Play as 26 new characters, and on 18 unique boards from iconic locations within Kirby's Return to Dreamland!

Use Parsec to play online with friends using Dolphin Emulator!

Download: https://gamebanana.com/mods/574572
Installation Instructions & Credits: https://bit.ly/KSINSTRUCTIONS
CSMM 7.2.1: https://github.com/FortuneStreetModding/csmm-qt/releases/tag/7.2.1
